once you get to higher levels<br>
<br>
Ill use Velks Lab for example, Kobolds<br>
<br>
Lets say your fighting a Kobold Warrior<br>
<br>
It has about 16khps and hits for dual 180 every 2.0 secs<br>
you have 2800hps with full buffs<br>
Warrior is doing using lammy class weaps.. so hes hitting for 35 a swing. taunting every 20 secs or so. on a .5 sec delay<br>
<br>
IF you dropped the BOmb so to speak that mob would aggro you and kill you before the warrior could taunt it off.. unless you got lucky and slipped a concuss in... THEN the warrior has a CHANCE of taunting off you..  <br>
By using smaller quicker draughts.. you can do the same damage, yet you can control the aggro better, hitting for mulitple nukes, and playing close to the edge of the aggro <p>Lleauaric Fyrewynd<br>Evoker<br>Knight of Eternal Wrath<br>Ayonae Ro<br> <img srg="http://www.goallineart.com/Payton,%20Walter.jpeg" border="0"></a>


